event.description:
In regards to the new regulations recently implemented, our supermarket department will be trading as usual, while we will be only be offering takeaway options from our Cafe.
Don’t forget our menu is available on UberEats as well!
To protect the health and well-being of our customers and staff, as of today, we will be limiting the amount of people entering the store.
We thank you sincerely for your patience and support during this time.
